# Mantis frontend (Vite) — copy to `.env` or `.env.local` and adjust if needed.
#
# Main API (FastAPI app under backend/)
VITE_API_BASE=http://localhost:8000
#
# Debate, Roadmap, and Podcast agents (FastAPI app under research_agent/)
# Do not set this to the same URL as VITE_API_BASE unless you have merged both APIs into one server.
VITE_RESEARCH_AGENT_BASE=http://localhost:8001
#
# Dev alternative: same-origin proxy (see frontend/vite.config.ts)
# VITE_RESEARCH_AGENT_BASE=/research-agent
